    "actor_description": "It hits and my thoughts simply\u2026 fail to line up. I can feel the weight of it somewhere behind my ribs, but my mind keeps sliding off the meaning like it can\u2019t get purchase. The world goes a little unreal\u2014sounds distant, edges too sharp\u2014while I keep moving on autopilot. I\u2019m here, I\u2019m looking, but it hasn\u2019t finished becoming true inside me.",
    "description_text": "{actor} goes suddenly still in a strangely intact way\u2014eyes fixed, face drained, as if they\u2019re waiting for the feeling to render. Their movements turn mechanical and delayed, like they\u2019re following instructions rather than inhabiting them.",
