            "failure_message": "Requires moderate grief with a stunned/blanking signature (numbness present or sadness rising), grounded in negative valence and low-to-mid arousal (not shutdown-flat). Blocks dissociation so the actor remains present, and caps despair so it stays early-onset shock rather than hopeless collapse. Triggers only on a grief spike or a sharp valence drop to prevent spam."
